# Keep the docker build context small. The node image (docker/node/Dockerfile) only needs
# pdn-app/<arch>/ (staged by scripts/docker-image.sh) + docker/node/. Everything else —
# including the raw artifacts/ trees the staging copies FROM — is excluded.
.git
**/obj
**/bin
**/node_modules
**/.vs
artifacts
tools
src
tests
web
